"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-02-13-lionel-messi-play-argentina-this-summers-olympics-20269196\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Lionel Messicould play at this summer's ParisOlympicsas one of three permitted over-age players after being invited to join theArgentina squadby Javier Mascherano.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javier Mascherano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheWorld Cupholders pulled off a 1-0 victory over Brazil on Sunday evening which secured their participation at Paris 2024 and denied the Selecao a place at the competition for the first time since 2004.\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 215, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999305968446471, \"rank\": 6.940795676548347e-05, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil had won the last two Olympic gold medals and were bidding to make it three in a row, but they will not get the chance to defend their title.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999305968446471, \"rank\": 6.940795676548347e-05, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Luciano Gondou's 77th-minute header secured the win for Argentina's Under-23 side in the South American qualifying tournament, and they are now expected to put together a strong line-up for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.601754000817058e-13, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_FIFA_World_Cup_qualification_(CONMEBOL)\", \"score\": 0.9180327868743372, \"rank\": 0.0892857142857348, \"text\": \"South American qualifying tournament\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_FIFA_World_Cup_qualification_(CONMEBOL)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2006_FIFA_World_Cup_qualification_(CONMEBOL)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teams are allowed to bring three players over the age of 23 and head coach Mascherano - who actually won gold alongside Messi in Beijing in 2008 - would love to include his old team-mate.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 844, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1157632181346626e-58, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.0902345036503644e-12, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Everyone already knows my relationship with Leo, the friendship I have,' said the former Barcelona midfielder after securing Olympic qualification.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 1061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"score\": 0.9999857834760514, \"rank\": 1.0913466245221907e-05, \"text\": \"Leo\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leo_Wyatt\"}, {\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.655251609492823e-27, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'A player like him has the doors open to accompany us [at the Olympics], then it will obviously depend on him and his commitments.'\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro's Head of Sport James Goldman delivers punchy analysis, transfer talk and his take on the week's biggest stories direct to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Goldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q28389\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up here, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentina's Under-23 captain, Thiago Almada, also welcomed the potential for Messi to be involved: 'I hope he has the desire, that he can be there.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1383, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.601754000817058e-13, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thiago_Almada\", \"score\": 0.9999998152616343, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thiago Almada\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thiago_Almada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thiago_Almada\"}, {\"begin\": 1460, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1157632181346626e-58, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We have to see how he is at that time, it would be a dream that he would be able to play.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If Messi comes, I will give him the captain's armband, obviously.'\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1157632181346626e-58, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Messi could be double-booked, however, with the 36-year-old having already expressed a desire to compete at the Copa America, which runs from June 20 to July 14.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1157632181346626e-58, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If Argentina reach the final, Messi would only have 10 days off before the Olympic tournament begins on July 24.\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1857, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 2.601754000817058e-13, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1157632181346626e-58, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should Messi accept the invite, he could come up against former Paris Saint-Germain team-mate Kylian Mbappe who has expressed a desire to take part at the home Games - and could even be his nation's flag bearer.\", \"from\": 1968, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1157632181346626e-58, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}, {\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999999992310222, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kylian Mbappe\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have always had the \\\"Olympic flame\\\".\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with the FIFA World Cup, the Olympic Games are the biggest sports event in the world,' he said earlier this year.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2340, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Games in Paris, 100 years after [the last time they were held in the city]\\u2026 mean the world to me.\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2356, \"end\": 2361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.257215717590545e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The idea of competing at the Games with France would be an extraordinary opportunity.\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2485, \"end\": 2491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0588152477762463e-19, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's actually more of a dream than an opportunity.'\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2704, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Marathon world record holder Kelvin Kiptum